<title>yạ ḥyạẗ ạlqlb</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- yạ ḥyạẗ ạlqlb yạ ḥbyb rwḥy ḍạmny
 ạ̹n mḍy̱ ạlạ̉hl stbqy̱ ạ̉nt ly tḍmny
 fyk yạ nbʿ srwry .. fyk ạ̉nt ldẖty
 ạ̉nsẖd mạ dmt mwjwdaⁿạ hnạ trnymty
 ạlqrạr- frḥy fyk lạ ynthy .. wly fyk mạ ạ̉sẖthy
 frḥty yạ nṣrty .. frḥ rby qwty
 lạ swạk bhjty .. (frḥy fyk)2
 (frḥy fyk lạ ynthy)2
 2- fyk qd wdʿt ḥzny .. wạḍṭrạby ạ̉bdaⁿạ
 fyk yạ rạʿy ḥyạty .. lạ ạḥtyạj ạ̉bdaⁿạ
 ly mʿ ạlạ̉yạm fy ạlậlạm .. ʿhdaⁿạ qd rsạ
 rby bạlʿzạʾ llạ̉frạḥ .. qlby krsạ
 3- lys mạ tʿṭy lnfsy .. ysẖgẖlny hhnạ
 ạ̉nt mwḍwʿ ạnsẖgẖạly .. wsjwdy wạltẖnạ
 fyk yạ kl ṭmwḥy .. ly rjạʾuⁿ qd smạ
 ạ̉kml hnạk ạ̉frạḥy .. ʿyạnaⁿạ fy ạlsmạ</lyrics>
</song>